## Examples

<span data-ttu-id="0ad73-239">次の例では、ReceiveSynchronously 値を取得します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ad73-239">This example gets the ReceiveSynchronously value.</span></span>

```csharp
